      "title": "Cricketer Praveen has Corona",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A senior official from the Sri Lanka Cricket Institute said that spinner Praveen Jayawickrama, who represents the Sri Lankan Test squad, has been diagnosed with Corona virus.",
        "The official added that none of the other players in the Sri Lankan squad have been confirmed to be infected with Corona."
      ],
